The following solves the ordering problem:

\makeatletter
\def\@@sumprimea_#1^#2{\sum_{#1}^{#2}\sumstrut'}
\def\@sumprimea_#1{\@ifnextchar^{\@@sumprimea_{#1}}{\@@sumprimea_{#1}^{}}}
