yes, that's a possible way. However, there is another, maybe nicer one;-)
You can type them directly - and LaTeX and PdfLaTeX will understand them
- when you use the package "inputenc". However, there you have to be
careful: As the binary values of those characters depend on the file
encoding (iso8859-1,latin15,UTF-8,...):
